      <title>顶级瑞银策略师认为2025年美国收益零的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/top-ubs-strategist-sees-risk-of-zero-us-earnings-growth-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银投资银行（UBS Investment Bank）的首席策略师表示，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税可能会锤击消费者的需求，这可能导致S＆amp; P 500公司今年绝对没有收入增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/top-ubs-strategist-sees-risk-of-zero-us-earnings-growth-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
