    <item>
      <title>石油老板说，特朗普政府在溃败中更好地制定计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/oil-boss-says-trump-administration-better-have-a-plan-amid-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Diamondback Energy Inc.的高管呼吁唐纳德·特朗普总统的政府解释全球贸易战争将如何帮助页岩生产商，这是美国石油老板的公众推翻的罕见实例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/oil-boss-says-trump-administration-better-have-a-plan-amid-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:55:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度贸易部长皮尤什·戈亚尔（Piyush Goyal）看到特朗普关税的机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/india-trade-minister-sees-opportunity-in-trump-tariffs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度商务部长皮尤什·戈亚尔（Piyush Goyal）向彭博社（Bloomberg）讲述了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的最新关税以及可能对增长的影响。他就贸易中断的短期挑战，加深与美国的贸易关系以及对中国在孟买印度全球论坛上的炉边聊天期间对中国不公平的贸易做法的担忧对他的短期挑战进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/india-trade-minister-sees-opportunity-in-trump-tariffs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德（BlackRock）的芬克（Fink）今年有四个美联储削减的机会零</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/blackrock-s-fink-zero-chance-of-four-fed-cuts-this-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BlackRock首席执行官拉里·芬克（Larry Fink）表示，他担心在纽约经济俱乐部的埃里克·沙茨克（Erik Schatzker）采访中，通货膨胀率提高和较高的利率。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-07/blackrock-s-fink-zero-chance-of-four-fed-cuts-this-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:49:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普指示安全小组审查美国钢铁交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）下令对美国钢铁公司的潜在出售给Nippon Steel Corp.进行另一项审查，开门，修改其前任乔·拜登（Joe Biden）的决定，以阻止141亿美元的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/trump-directs-security-panel-to-review-us-steel-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 14:21:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一小时停赛后，华沙巴尔斯恢复交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/warsaw-bourse-suspends-trade-due-to-volatility-high-volumes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周一停职超过一个小时的停赛之后，华沙证券交易所恢复了所有市场的交易，这在波动性和销量激增的情况下，这使得“安全原因”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/warsaw-bourse-suspends-trade-due-to-volatility-high-volumes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:54:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银（UBS）认为，我们的信用价差达到自2020年以来的最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/ubs-sees-bond-spreads-widening-to-levels-last-seen-in-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团（UBS Group AG）战略家预计，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税会产生影响，将企业债务扩散到大流行初期的最后水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/ubs-sees-bond-spreads-widening-to-levels-last-seen-in-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 13:03:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税战争升级时，中国股票“恐慌销售”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者为自己的影响，中国股价暴跌，主权收益率略低，因为投资者因世界上两个最大经济体之间的螺旋贸易冲突而陷入困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/chinese-stocks-plunge-amid-growing-fear-of-full-blown-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 01:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>本周全球商品观看的五个关键图表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在为商品市场进行了少量交易，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的全球影响将继续成为本周贸易商的首要影响。当采矿界将于本周在智利举行的主要铜业聚会前进，情况就是如此。同时，税款可能会使美国人更昂贵。石油市场正在面对一两次需求问题，欧佩克+的供应更多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/five-key-charts-to-watch-in-global-commodity-markets-this-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
